Start the server program in the background.
  $ dune exe ../src/server/server.exe > /dev/null &
  $ PORT=8082

Capture it's process id.
  $ PID=`echo $!`

Wait (max 5 sec) for server to start
  $ TIMEOUT=5
  $ URL=localhost:$PORT/_health
  $ ./wait_server_up.sh "$URL"
